### 1. ENTITIES

**Location:** `C:\projects\develop_blog\backend\devblog\devblog\src\main\java\met\ivan\devblog\entity\`

#### **User.java**
- **ID Strategy:** `@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)`
- **Fields:**
  - `Long id` (primary key)
  - `String username` (unique, max 50)
  - `String email` (unique, max 100)
  - `String passwordHash` (not null)
  - `String displayName` (max 100)
  - `String bio` (max 500)
  - `String avatarUrl` (max 255)
  - `boolean active` (default: true)
  - `Instant createdAt` (@CreationTimestamp, immutable)
  - `Instant updatedAt` (@UpdateTimestamp)
  - `Long version` (@Version for optimistic locking)
- **Relationships:** `@ManyToMany Set&lt;Role&gt; roles` (LAZY, join table: user_roles)
- **Auditing:** CreationTimestamp, UpdateTimestamp
- **Indexes:** idx_users_username, idx_users_email

#### **Post.java**
- **ID Strategy:** `@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)`
- **Fields:**
  - `Long id` (primary key)
  - `String title` (not null, max 255)
  - `String slug` (unique, max 300) — URL-safe identifier
  - `String contentMarkdown` (not null, TEXT)
  - `String excerpt` (max 300)
  - `PostStatus status` (DRAFT/PUBLISHED, default: DRAFT)
  - `Long viewCount` (default: 0L) — **implemented as simple Long field, incremented via @Modifying @Query in repository**
  - `Instant publishedAt` (null until published)
  - `Instant createdAt` (@CreationTimestamp)
  - `Instant updatedAt` (@UpdateTimestamp)
  - `Long version` (@Version)
  - `Set&lt;String&gt; tags` (@ElementCollection with CollectionTable)
- **Relationships:**
  - `@ManyToOne(LAZY) User author` (required, join column: author_id)
  - `@ManyToOne(LAZY) Category category` (optional)
- **Auditing:** CreationTimestamp, UpdateTimestamp
- **Indexes:** idx_posts_slug, idx_posts_status, idx_posts_author_id, idx_post_tags_tag

#### **Category.java**
- **ID Strategy:** `@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)`
- **Fields:**
  - `Long id`
  - `String name` (unique, max 100)
  - `String slug` (unique, max 120) — generated from name
  - `String description` (TEXT)
  - `Instant createdAt` (@CreationTimestamp)
  - `Instant updatedAt` (@UpdateTimestamp)
- **Auditing:** CreationTimestamp, UpdateTimestamp
- **Indexes:** idx_categories_slug

#### **RefreshToken.java**
- **ID Strategy:** `@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)`
- **Fields:**
  - `Long id`
  - `String token` (unique, max 512)
  - `Instant expiresAt` (not null)
  - `boolean revoked` (default: false) — for token rotation
- **Relationships:** `@ManyToOne(LAZY) User user` (required)
- **Indexes:** idx_refresh_token_token, idx_refresh_token_user

#### **Role.java**
- **ID Strategy:** `@GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)`
- **Fields:**
  - `Long id`
  - `RoleName name` (enum, unique, ADMIN/USER)

