### 2. DTOs

**Location:** `C:\projects\develop_blog\backend\devblog\devblog\src\main\java\met\ivan\devblog\dto\`

#### **Create/Update Post DTOs**
- **CreatePostRequest:** title, contentMarkdown, excerpt, categoryId, status (optional), tags (Set, max 10 tags)
- **UpdatePostRequest:** title, contentMarkdown, excerpt, categoryId, tags (no status field—use separate endpoint)
- **UpdatePostStatusRequest:** status field (for changing DRAFT↔PUBLISHED)

#### **Response DTOs**
- **PostResponse:** Full DTO with contentMarkdown included
  - Fields: id, slug, title, excerpt, status, category (CategoryResponse), author (AuthorSummary), publishedAt, createdAt, contentMarkdown, updatedAt, tags, viewCount
  - Uses `@JsonInclude(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)` for optional fields
  
- **PostSummaryResponse:** For list views (excludes contentMarkdown)
  - Fields: id, slug, title, excerpt, status, category, author, publishedAt, createdAt, tags, viewCount

- **AuthorSummary:** id, username, displayName (minimal author info in post responses)

- **CategoryResponse:** id, name, slug, description

- **UserResponse:** id, username, email, displayName, bio, avatarUrl, roles (List&lt;String&gt;), active, createdAt

#### **Pagination**
- Uses Spring Data `Page&lt;PostSummaryResponse&gt;` for list endpoints
- `@PageableDefault(size = 20)` annotation on pageable parameters
- Clients pass `?page=0&amp;size=20&amp;sort=field,desc`

