### 3. CONTROLLERS

**Location:** `C:\projects\develop_blog\backend\devblog\devblog\src\main\java\met\ivan\devblog\controller\`

#### **PostController** (`/api/posts`)
```
GET    /api/posts
       Params: ?category=slug, ?search=query, ?sort=latest|popular, page/size
       Public endpoint, returns Page&lt;PostSummaryResponse&gt;

GET    /api/posts/{slug}
       Public, returns PostResponse + increments viewCount
       Throws ResourceNotFoundException if not published

GET    /api/posts/mine
       Authenticated, Params: ?status=DRAFT|PUBLISHED
       Returns user's own posts (all statuses)

GET    /api/posts/mine/{id}
       Authenticated, owner or admin only
       Returns full PostResponse

POST   /api/posts
       Authenticated, @RequestBody CreatePostRequest
       Returns PostResponse with created post

PUT    /api/posts/{id}
       Authenticated, owner or admin only
       Updates post (slug remains stable)

PUT    /api/posts/{id}/status
       Authenticated, owner or admin only
       Changes DRAFT↔PUBLISHED, sets publishedAt when publishing

DELETE /api/posts/{id}
       Authenticated, owner or admin only
       Hard delete
```

**Auth Pattern:** `@AuthenticationPrincipal UserDetails principal` — principal.getUsername() is used to resolve the current user

#### **UserController** (`/api/users`)
