POST   /api/auth/register
       Public, @RequestBody RegisterRequest
       Returns AuthResponse (accessToken, refreshToken, user)

POST   /api/auth/login
       Public, @RequestBody LoginRequest (usernameOrEmail, password)
       Returns AuthResponse

POST   /api/auth/refresh
       Public, @RequestBody RefreshTokenRequest
       Implements token rotation (revokes old, issues new)
